## PHASE 5 : RESPONSIVE (mobile-first v0 strategy)

### Breakpoints (dÃ©jÃ  dÃ©finis tokens)

- Mobile: < 640px
- Tablet: 640px - 1024px
- Desktop: > 1024px

### Adaptations clÃ©s

**Typography scale down :**
- H1 : 96px â 48px mobile
- H2 : 60px â 36px mobile
- Body : 16px â 15px mobile

**Layout :**
- Grid 3-col â 1-col mobile
- Padding 80px â 20px mobile
- Hero input : width 100% mobile

**Navigation mobile :**
- Hamburger menu
- Full-screen drawer
- Bottom-to-top animation

---

## GARDE-FOUS CRITIQUES

### 1. PERFORMANCE
- Lazy-load ProjectCard images (Next Image)
- Code splitting routes
- Preload critical fonts
- LCP < 2.5s (target v0)

### 2. ACCESSIBILITÃ
